762
00:58:39,307 --> 00:58:41,184
Saya fikir anda akhirnya
mula bernafas semula,

763
00:58:42,310 --> 00:58:44,854
tapi saya nampak awak ada

764
00:58:50,944 --> 00:58:55,823
